WEBVTT

1
01:03:11.200 --> 01:03:14.120 
我已经赔付了给你 我已经送了个人给你当水手
You have my payment. One soul to serve on your ship.

2
01:03:14.250 --> 01:03:16.750 
两个灵魂不能混为一谈
One soul is not equal to another.

3
01:03:17.580 --> 01:03:24.090 
我们已经达成了共识 接下来我们谈谈价钱吧
We've established my proposal is sound in principle. Now we're haggling over price.

4
01:03:24.220 --> 01:03:26.760 
价钱?
Price?

5
01:03:28.800 --> 01:03:32.270 
我的灵魂需要多少人来换
Just how many souls do you think my soul is worth?

6
01:03:36.060 --> 01:03:38.690 
一百人的灵魂
One hundred souls.

7
01:03:39.650 --> 01:03:41.400 
三天时间
Three days.

